Its like a mix of vampire survivors and asteroids. level up get stronger and faster.
Now with "Threshold Synergies": Stacking stats (Speed, HP, FireRate) unlocks unexpected abilities.
Rebalanced upgrades: Minigun (Kinetic/Heat), Sniper (One-Shot), and Titanium Hull (Crowd Control).
New Enemies: Trailblazer (leaves hazardous trail) and Nullifier (absorbs player bullets).
Reflector now deflects enemy projectiles.
New: Hive (spawns drone swarms) and Skirmisher (dodges player bullets).
New Abilities: Mines (explosive traps), Orbital Laser (strikes from the sky), and Adrenaline (Combo-based power).
New Ultimate: Chrono Breaker (Freezes time for enemies).
New Tech: Gravity Well (Black holes) and Wildcard (Infinite stat scaling).
